The Proposal:
Jakartaveer Hindkesari Maruti Mane was a world-renowned wrestler. They've got their
His career has brightened India's name on the world stage. He made a seminal contribution to the field of wrestling.
The government has approved the construction of a memorial for the legendary wrestler at his native place Kavtepiran, Taluka-Miraj, District-Sangli. Memorial Committee constituted under 25.7.2011
Some of the honorable members of this committee have died. Against this background, as well as the current situation

A proposal to reconstitute the committee was submitted to the government by the Collector, Sangli, with the necessary changes. Accordingly, the issue of approving the reconstitution of the memorial committee was under the consideration of the government.
The government's decision:

It has been decided to reconstitute the memorial committee for the memorial of Hindkesari Maruthi Mane, an international wrestler, in his native village Kavtepiran, Taluka Miraj, District Sangli as follows.
